text: Cariba Heine (born October 1, 1988) is an actress who acts in movies and in television. She was born in Johannesburg, South Africa, and was raised in Australia. She played Bridget Sanchez in the movie Blue Water High. She also had many other movies. ==References== Category:Australian movie actors Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:People from Johannesburg
